Maven:
======
Apache Maven is a software project management and comprehension tool. 
It is based on the concept of a project object model (POM),
Maven can manage a project's build, reporting and documentation.

Build Tools:
  java : 
    MAVEN/
    ANt/
    Gradle     
.Net:
----
  NaNt
  MSBuild
JAVASCRIPT:
-----------
  Gulp
  Grunt
